			"type": "text",
			"content": "<span> </span><p>och de om funktionsstörningar i</p>tyreoidea<a href=\"#17890\" class=\"btn btn-primary btn-mini pageLink\"><i class=\"fa fa-arrow-right fa-white\"></i></a><p>).</p><div class=\"clearfix\"></div>",
